snippet.title: Domiverse - How to play - Xand
snippet.description:
How to play Xand

For centuries, people of Nili and Xand make war. He devasted Nili’s planet with his army.
When xand is not using his machinegun with limited ammo, he can slice with his knife. To make it sneaky, he can drop an exploding clone while he’s moving invisible.

http://domiverse.be

Steam store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/598880/Domiverse/
